snippet.title: Slime Rancher - Mochi's Megabucks Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Mochi’s Megabucks Update is here! This Slime Rancher update invites you to explore the Nimble Valley: a new zone that is home to the exceedingly rare quicksilver slimes. Not much is known about the Valley outside of the fact that it is owned by the one and only Mochi Miles. Work for Mochi and prove yourself to be a first-rate rancher!

Available NOW!

Full patch notes: http://forums.monomipark.com/viewtopic.php?f=10&t=6617

Get Slime Rancher merchandise: http://slimerancher.com/merch

Buy on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/433340/Slime_Rancher

Developed by Monomi Park
www.slimerancher.com
www.monomipark.com
Follow us on Twitter: @monomipark
